CENTER FOR CONSTITUTIONAL RIGHTS, et al., petitioners,
v.
Barack H. OBAMA, President of United States, et al. No. 13-802. Supreme Court of the United States March 3, 2014.

Case below, Azatyan v. Holder, 522 Fed.Appx. 383.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
